svg.title: Personal Budget Tracker - Class Diagram with OCL Constraints

g.text: Personal Budget Tracker - Class Diagram with OCL Constraints
{OCL} inv uniqueEmail: User.allInstances()->forAll(u1, u2 | u1 <> u2 implies u1.email <> u2.email)
{OCL} inv nonNegativeBalance: self.type <> AccountType::CREDIT_CARD_ACCOUNT implies self.balance >= 0
{OCL} inv uniqueAccountNamePerUser: Account.allInstances()->forAll(a1, a2 | a1 <> a2 and a1.userId = a2.userId implies a1.name <> a2.name)
{OCL} inv uniqueCategoryNamePerUser: Category.allInstances()->forAll(c1, c2 | c1 <> c2 and c1.userId = c2.userId implies c1.name <> c2.name)
{OCL} inv accountAndCategoryBelongToUser: self.userId = self.account.userId and self.userId = self.category.userId
{OCL} pre userCanOnlyUpdateOwnProfile: let currentUser = SecurityContextHolder.getContext().getAuthentication().getPrincipal() in currentUser.id = id
{OCL} pre userCanOnlyDeleteOwnProfile: let currentUser = SecurityContextHolder.getContext().getAuthentication().getPrincipal() in currentUser.id = id

{OCL} post accountBalanceRestoredAfterDeleteExpense: let entry = EntryRepository.findById(id) in entry.expense implies AccountService.findById(entry.account.id).balance = AccountService.findById(entry.account.id).balance@pre + entry.amount

{OCL} post accountBalanceReducedAfterDeleteIncome: let entry = EntryRepository.findById(id) in not entry.expense implies AccountService.findById(entry.account.id).balance = AccountService.findById(entry.account.id).balance@pre - entry.amount
